"title": "3278: Holy Spirit, indwelling of",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "3278: holy spirit, indwelling of",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>The Holy Spirit dwells within Jesus Christ and his disciples. Recognisable results in believers' lives include Christlikeness and the fruit of the Spirit.</p>\n<h2>The indwelling of the Holy Spirit in the OT</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen41:38\">GEN 41:38</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod35:31\">EXO 35:31</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num27:18\">NUM 27:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam10:6-1Sam10:7\">1SA 10:6–10:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa59:21\">ISA 59:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hag2:5\">HAG 2:5</a></p>\n<h2>The Holy Spirit indwells Jesus Christ</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa11:2\">ISA 11:2</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt12:18\">MAT 12:18</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa42:1\">ISA 42:1</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke4:18\">LUK 4:18</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa61:1\">ISA 61:1</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts10:38\">ACT 10:38</a></p>\n<h2>The indwelling of the Holy Spirit is promised to believers</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John14:17\">JHN 14:17</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek36:27\">EZK 36:27</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek37:14\">EZK 37:14</a></p>\n<h2>The Holy Spirit indwells believers</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim1:14\">2TI 1:14</a></strong> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor3:16\">1CO 3:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor6:19\">1CO 6:19</a>; \n<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph2:22\">EPH 2:22</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John2:27\">1JN 2:27</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John3:24\">1JN 3:24</a></p>\n<h2>Results of the Holy Spirit's indwelling in believers</h2>\n<h3>The Holy Spirit guarantees life</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom8:11\">ROM 8:11</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek37:14\">EZK 37:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John7:38-John7:39\">JHN 7:38–7:39</a></p>\n<h3>The Holy Spirit assures believers that they belong to God</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom8:14-Rom8:16\">ROM 8:14–8:16</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor1:21-2Cor1:22\">2CO 1:21–1:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal4:6\">GAL 4:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph1:13-Eph1:14\">EPH 1:13–1:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John4:13\">1JN 4:13</a></p>\n<h3>Wisdom and insight are received</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen41:38\">GEN 41:38</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut34:9\">DEU 34:9</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan4:8-Dan4:9\">DAN 4:8–4:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan4:18\">DAN 4:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan5:11\">DAN 5:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan5:14\">DAN 5:14</a></p>\n<h3>Strength is received</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph3:16\">EPH 3:16</a></p>\n<h3>Preaching and public testimony is aided</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt10:20\">MAT 10:20</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark13:11\">MRK 13:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke12:12\">LUK 12:12</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts4:8-Acts4:12\">ACT 4:8–4:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts5:29-Acts5:32\">ACT 5:29–5:32</a></p>\n<h3>The moral law is obeyed</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek36:27\">EZK 36:27</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom8:4-Rom8:5\">ROM 8:4–8:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom8:13\">ROM 8:13</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal5:16\">GAL 5:16</a></p>\n<h3>The fruit of the Spirit is displayed</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal5:22-Gal5:23\">GAL 5:22–5:23</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom5:5\">ROM 5:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom14:17\">ROM 14:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom15:13\">ROM 15:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom15:30\">ROM 15:30</a></p>\n<h2>Those without the Holy Spirit's indwelling are not Christlike</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal5:17\">GAL 5:17</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jude1:18-Jude1:19\">JUD 1:18–1:19</a></p>",
